candle-gen-sana is an independent, from-scratch Rust/candle reimplementation of
the SANA (NVlabs) text-to-image architecture — the DC-AE f32 deep-compression
autoencoder, the Linear-DiT trunk, and the gemma-2-2b-it CHI caption encoder
seam. It does not include or redistribute any model weights.

